This README file contains information on the contents of the meta-tis-tdx-cameras layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.

Dependencies
============

  URI: https://git.toradex.com/meta-toradex-bsp-common.git
  branch: scarthgap-7.x.y


Patches and Support
===================

Please direct support requests regarding this layer or The Imaging Source sensor
modules to this email adress:

support@theimagingsource.com

Please submit any patches against the meta-tis-tdx-cameras layer to the maintainer:

Maintainer: Arne Caspari <arne.caspari@theimagingsource.com>


Adding the meta-tis-tdx-cameras layer to your build
=================================================

Run 'bitbake-layers add-layer meta-tis-tdx-cameras'

Layer Description
=================

This layer contains the devicetree overlay files and kernel patches neccessary
to use The Imaging Source MIPI sensor modules on Toradex SoMs.

Supported Platforms
===================

This layer supports the following platforms:

 - verdin-imx8mp


Supported Sensor Modules
========================

This layer supports the following sensor modules:

 - Dxx 36SX290
 - Dxx 36SX462
 - Dxx 36SX296
 - Dxx 36SX297
 - Dxx 36SR0521
